text: Sireethorn Leearamwat (born 4 December 1993) is a Thai model, pharmacist and Miss International 2019. She is the first woman from Thailand to win Miss International. She is also Miss Thailand 2019. == Biography == Sireethorn Leearamwat was born in Bangkok, Thailand. She studied at Mahidol University, where she got a Bachelo degree in Pharmacy. After finishing the university, she worked as a pharmacist. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1993 births Category:Beauty pageant winners Category:Thai people
